Okay, i dont normally admit this but this video alone has been viewed by me like 50 times the past 2 days, no exagerration.
My opinion is: the producers and the the judges had consensus not to give him the golden buzzer to give him more chances of perfomorming on stage to get more views which is certain.
Whether he wins or not, AGT awes him big time BUT Marcelito is already very lucky enough to have been given this opportunity to show his talent to the world.
His talent is one in a million (if not one in a billion, literally).
He deserves such high praise and recognition.
He is a very humble person and i hope he doesnt change this attritube of his.
I do hope he will win, as i dont see any reason why he cant if the results will be based on voting.
